♪Thinking of you,
the sky turns light blue♪

2
00:00:21,060 --> 00:00:24,620
♪Thinking of you,
the sunlight feels gentle♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:28,820
♪Thinking of you, the clouds look pink♪

4
00:00:29,780 --> 00:00:33,140
♪One bite, so sweet♪

5
00:00:35,940 --> 00:00:40,660
♪Loving you
is like honey melting in the sun♪

6
00:00:40,900 --> 00:00:44,900
♪Even the coldest winter feels warm♪

7
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:50,780
♪Since falling for you,
I only want your company♪

8
00:00:51,060 --> 00:00:54,940
♪You see through
all my sweet little schemes♪

9
00:00:55,260 --> 00:00:57,340
♪What should I do?♪

10
00:01:00,220 --> 00:01:06,100
[My Sassy Girl]

11
00:01:06,780 --> 00:01:09,100
[Episode 3]

12
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,440
Ji Xinshi.

13
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,880
Let me guess.

14
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,360
You packed this medicine?

15
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:37,840
Exactly.

16
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:39,800
Lord Lin.

17
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,360
What's wrong with it?

18
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:42,920
My Lord.

19
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:54,120
Familiar with it?

20
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:58,080
This is the red silk knot
used to hang Ji Fanghai.

21
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:01,320
It is a rare chevron knot.

22
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,120
You tied the knot the same way

23
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,440
you wrapped the medicine.

24
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:07,960
Do you want to confess it?

25
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,000
Lord Lin.

26
00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:12,560
With just one knot,

27
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,280
can you convict me of the crime?

28
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:23,000
Of course not.

29
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,240
For the scar on your palm,

30
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:27,880
how do you explain it?

31
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,320
I got hurt when crushing the medicine
two days ago.

32
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,040
Workers in Virtue Hall

33
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,680
can prove it.

34
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,000
When you killed Bao Sheng,

35
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:42,280
Bao Sheng resisted

36
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,960
and scratched your palm.

37
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:49,400
So you intentionally hurt your palm

38
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:51,240
to cover up the scratches.

39
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,000
Am I right?

40
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,040
Lord Lin.

41
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,440
Without evidence,

42
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,920
you cannot convict me of a crime
with deduction.

43
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:03,120
You are trampling on human lives.

44
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,120
I don't buy it.

45
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:07,480
Let's talk about the murder weapon.

46
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,720
Bao Sheng and Ji Fanghai

47
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:15,120
were killed with the same
curiously shaped blade.

48
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:16,960
After inspection,

49
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:20,120
The closest thing to the shape of it

50
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:23,960
is a physician's lancet.

51
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,160
Lei.

52
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,560
Go check Ji Xinshi's medicine box.

53
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,320
Yes.

54
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,520
My Lord.

55
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,760
No lancet.

56
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,520
Lord Lin.

57
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,080
You have no evidence.

58
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,240
You can't wrong a good man.

59
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,000
That is weird.

60
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,960
I've interrogated
all the physicians in Jinzhou.

61
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,880
None of their lancets

62
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:18,520
fit the wound of the deceased.

63
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,560
And at this time,

64
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,480
you lost yours.

65
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:23,840
Tell me.

66
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,400
Did you kill someone

67
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,360
and hide the lancet on purpose?

68
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:26,920
I didn't.

69
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:27,800
Where is the lancet?

70
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:28,360
I threw it.

71
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,640
Where and when?

72
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:30,400
I threw it at...

73
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,240
At...

74
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:33,680
In the well in the backyard.

75
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:37,440
I knew it.

76
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,640
This adopted son

77
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:39,960
must have some problem.

78
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:42,280
I used the murder weapon as a lure

79
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,280
to make the suspect show up.

80
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,120
Then I saw a man sneak around

81
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,840
and throw a lancet

82
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:51,200
into the backyard well.

83
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,120
Thanks to Fu Wenyuan,

84
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,480
he took a lot of effort

85
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,440
to get it out.

86
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:27,640
Its size must match the victim's wound.

87
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,960
Ji Xinshi.

88
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:33,080
Your statement
is full of inconsistencies and loopholes.

89
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,200
Now there are both witnesses
and physical evidence,

90
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:37,560
what else do you want to say?

91
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:39,880
Come on.

92
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,400
Arrest him.

93
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,240
Yes.

94
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:43,680
What's wrong?

95
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,280
What happened?

96
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:46,100
Lord Lin.

97
00:05:46,300 --> 00:05:47,040
What's up?

98
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:48,160
Ouch.

99
00:05:48,180 --> 00:05:48,660
Don't move.

100
00:05:48,660 --> 00:05:49,300
Ji Xinshi.

101
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,640
Don't come over.

102
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,360
Don't come over.

103
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,160
Actually, I don't want

104
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:55,240
to get anyone else involved in this.

105
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,720
But you guys push me
over and over again.

106
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,720
Calm down.

107
00:05:58,960 --> 00:05:59,920
Let Mr. Yu go.

108
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:01,720
Get me a fast horse.

109
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:02,640
When I arrived in the countryside,

110
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,280
I would let this old man go.

111
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:05,040
Otherwise,

112
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,360
I will kill him right now.

113
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,640
Lu.

114
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,440
Ji Xinshi.

115
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,640
Ji Fanghai is your adoptive father
who brought you up,

116
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:28,760
why did you kill him?

117
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,160
Adoptive father?

118
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,560
I was raised by my adoptive mother.

119
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,440
He...

120
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:40,480
He is nothing.

121
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:44,040
When I was seven years old,

122
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,400
both my parents passed away.

123
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,200
I didn't have the money to bury them.

124
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,280
I had to sell myself.

125
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,440
Ji Fanghai's wife

126
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,160
was good by nature.

127
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:56,920
Seeing me helpless,
she took me as an adopted son.

128
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,640
But the good times didn't last forever.

129
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:04,720
My adoptive mother
soon became terminally ill.

130
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:09,240
Ji Fanghai took my adoptive mother
as a burden.

131
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,480
After my adoptive mother
had her last breath,

132
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,920
she was about to be buried.

133
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,840
Ji Fanghai discovered

134
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:17,200
she still had a breath.

135
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,680
He...

136
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,380
[Funeral]

137
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:25,280
He was unwilling to take care of her

138
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:29,760
and strangled her to death.

139
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:33,400
She was strangled to death!

140
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:43,520
Ji Fanghai is a hypocrite.
He deserved it.

141
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,280
He shouldn't be respected.

142
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:52,000
Did you change my story book?

143
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,800
You've written so many story books.

144
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:59,520
People say that good and evil
will have their outcomes.

145
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,160
But I have waited so long,

146
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,280
and it never comes.

147
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:06,940
But killing someone
in imitation of your story books

148
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:10,200
is a good way to confuse the public.

149
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,540
I wrote the story books

150
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:16,060
to tell people to believe in justice.

151
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,480
If you don't believe it, it's fine.

152
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,120
But why did you set me up?

153
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,160
Ms. Lu.

154
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:23,640
In fact, there is no difference
between you and me.

155
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,560
The only difference is

156
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:28,840
that I kill with a knife,

157
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:31,820
and you kill with a pen.

158
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,280
Don't talk nonsense.

159
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:35,260
Plead your guilty now.

160
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:38,720
You killed Ji Fanghai
to avenge your adoptive mother.

161
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,000
Then why did you kill Bao Sheng?

162
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,920
He said he saw me kill Ji Fanghai

163
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:50,720
and asked me
to hand over the estate of Virtue Hall.

164
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:55,000
I was so angry

165
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:57,040
and I killed him.

166
00:08:57,720 --> 00:09:00,400
Then why did you stuff him in a coffin
and suffocate him to death?

167
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:01,740
That's cruel.

168
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,080
I just...

169
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:06,600
I just stabbed him with a knife.

170
00:09:06,860 --> 00:09:08,360
I didn't stuff him into a coffin.

171
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:10,720
The evidence is overwhelming.

172
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:11,880
Just admit it.

173
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,200
Forget it.

174
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,360
You don't believe me, anyway.

175
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,820
I am glad to know

176
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,480
that Bao Sheng

177
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,280
was tortured to death.

178
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:25,520
My Lord.

179
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,920
I will take my responsibility.

180
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:30,800
I, Ji Xinshi,

181
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,480
plead guilty.

182
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,560
My Lord.

183
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:38,600
Can the case be closed?

184
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,800
Put him in jail first.

185
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,000
Interrogate him another day.

186
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:43,760
Yes.

187
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,280
Take away.

188
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,160
Yes.

189
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:54,000
No regret.

190
00:09:57,020 --> 00:09:58,240
[Jinzhou Yamen]

191
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:58,960
My Lord.

192
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,860
[Confession]
This is Ji Xinshi's confession.

193
00:10:03,260 --> 00:10:04,940
Since the people heard
that the real murderer was arrested,

194
00:10:04,940 --> 00:10:06,320
they've been relieved.

195
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,880
I'll put up a notice as you say.

196
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:11,480
Disclose the facts of the two murders

197
00:10:11,680 --> 00:10:12,400
to calm the people down.

198
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,040
Yes.

199
00:10:13,300 --> 00:10:15,020
[Confession]

200
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,640
Ji Xinshi said

201
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,080
he didn't stuff Bao Sheng in the coffin.

202
00:10:20,460 --> 00:10:22,000
If it's true,
then who would have done it?

203
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:23,560
My Lord.

204
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:24,960
My Lord.

205
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:25,800
No good.

206
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,440
Ji Xinshi

207
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:28,440
committed suicide.

208
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:29,960
What?

209
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,320
As soon as he was in prison,

210
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:32,600
he hit the wall and died.

211
00:10:33,760 --> 00:10:35,360
We haven't finished the trial yet,

212
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:36,960
but he committed suicide.

213
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,000
Could it be

214
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:41,160
he wanted to cover up

215
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,640
for somebody?

216
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,800
Just in court,

217
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,800
I thought it was doubtful.

218
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:47,960
It looks like

219
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:49,080
Ji Xinshi

220
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,400
had another helper.

221
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,680
It seems

222
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,400
the murderers who imitate the story book

223
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,120
are more than one.

224
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,160
This is the medicine
I specially prepared.

225
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:10,800
It can ease your pain.

226
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:14,440
Thanks.

227
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,000
Since

228
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,400
I've cleared myself of suspicion,

229
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:20,000
there's no need for me to stay here.

230
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:21,680
From now on,

231
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:22,880
let's part ways.

232
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:24,960
We don't owe each other.

233
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,040
You left without saying goodbye
more than a year ago.

234
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,720
You haven't given me an explanation.

235
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,040
Explanation?

236
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:34,800
You broke your promise

237
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:37,080
by sending me a farewell letter.

238
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:39,160
You wanted to be with Wen Ruoxi.

239
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,440
How do you explain that?

240
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:42,880
I was the one who received
a farewell letter.

241
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:43,880
You make it wrong.

242
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:44,560
I didn't.

243
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:45,520
Lu.

244
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:50,600
Lord Lin.

245
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,240
I have to pick up Lu.

246
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:56,000
You hurt Lu so much.

247
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,040
Don't pester her anymore.

248
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,360
She has her own choice.

249
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,560
Let's go.

250
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,480
Lu.

251
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:08,440
Lu.

252
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:09,680
Let's go home.

253
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:10,600
Yes.

254
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,640
The case is closed.

255
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:40,000
Why do you still look upset?

256
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:44,000
He was my childhood sweetheart
for more than ten years.

257
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,960
But we have no good ending.

258
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:49,000
Isn't it worth a sigh?

259
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,360
Forget the ungrateful man.

260
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:52,560
He's not worth your sorrow.

261
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,000
Why don't you

262
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:55,560
think about

263
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:57,400
the future for us?

264
00:12:58,640 --> 00:12:59,520
The future for us?

265
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:00,880
Yeah, in the future,

266
00:13:02,520 --> 00:13:04,560
if you want to write any story book,

267
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:06,640
this story would be a great one.

268
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:11,320
I used to write them

269
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:13,200
as a means of earning a living.

270
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,240
I didn't expect

271
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:17,180
it can be used as a tool to kill.

272
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,480
As the saying goes,

273
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:20,760
Writings are for conveying truth.

274
00:13:21,680 --> 00:13:23,200
Maybe there is no point

275
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:25,200
for me to write the story.

276
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:29,080
Once people have an obsession,
they will sink deeper and deeper.

277
00:13:29,760 --> 00:13:31,320
The reason Ji Xinshi killed people

278
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,680
was not because of your story books,

279
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:36,840
but because he has too much hatred.

280
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:39,960
I figured it out.

281
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:41,680
From now on,

282
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,960
I'll never write
those murder stories again.

283
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:44,840
All right.

284
00:13:45,160 --> 00:13:46,040
Then

285
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,640
what plan

286
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:49,320
do you have?

287
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:51,040
I have thought about it.

288
00:13:52,040 --> 00:13:53,760
I will earn my esteem.

