347
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,080
I don't know.

348
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,520
Just half a year ago,

349
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:07,680
Ms. Jiang, Mr. Sun's daughter-in-law

350
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,880
