351
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:11,040
She flew into the sky.

352
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:12,400
Alas.

353
00:16:12,560 --> 00:16:14,240
Mr. Sun had an infatuation with her.

354
00:16:14,880 --> 00:16:15,600
At the top of the hill,

355
