356
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:19,160
Really?

357
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:23,560
The story sounds interesting.

358
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,240
Is it real?

359
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,720
A carp fairy.

360
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:29,360
This is interesting.

361
00:16:29,520 --> 00:16:30,400
Is it real?

362
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,320
Of course.

363
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,720
Just half a year ago,

364
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:34,960
The guests at the banquet saw it.

365
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:38,040
On the wedding night,

366
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:40,040
