Money for story.

375
00:16:59,680 --> 00:17:02,200
Collection of stories
about the carp fairy.

376
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:03,240
Let's come one by one.

377
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,760
I got it.

378
00:17:04,980 --> 00:17:06,640
Don't worry, everybody.

379
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,880
- One by one.
- Me.

380
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:08,680
You come first.

381
00:17:08,860 --> 00:17:10,280
For Mr. Sun's Wedding day,

382
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:11,160
I'm on the spot.

383
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:13,780
His wife turned into a carp fairy.

384
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:16,040
Her tail was golden.

385
00:17:16,120 --> 00:17:17,000
It's true.

386
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,560
At that time, many people saw it.

387
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:19,340
Right?

388
00:17:19,340 --> 00:17:21,400
- It's my turn.
- It's my turn.

389
00:17:23,600 --> 00:17:24,180
Come on.

390
00:17:24,180 --> 00:17:24,780
Thanks.

391
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:27,200
Please let me.

392
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,200
Let me.

393
