Wait a minute.

394
00:17:29,100 --> 00:17:30,080
Don't worry.

395
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:31,940
I'll go first.

396
00:17:31,940 --> 00:17:32,920
Wait a minute.

397
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:35,800
Do you know

398
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:38,200
why the bride could become immortal?

399
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:40,440
Why?

400
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:41,800
That's because

401
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:43,040
she took

402
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:44,560
the immortal pill

403
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:46,280
that I made.

404
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:50,120
For the pill,

405
00:17:50,320 --> 00:17:50,960
it just needs

406
00:17:51,280 --> 00:17:52,360
two liang of broken silver.

407
00:17:52,840 --> 00:17:54,080
You can take it for two months.

408
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:58,240
Thank you.

409
