It's real.

412
00:18:04,280 --> 00:18:04,840
It's real.

413
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:05,560
Next one.

414
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,340
Me.

415
00:18:07,520 --> 00:18:08,240
This one.

416
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:11,280
Listen to me.

417
00:18:14,440 --> 00:18:15,200
What they say

418
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:17,320
is not true.

419
00:18:18,940 --> 00:18:20,400
There's no such thing

420
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:22,840
as a living person becoming immortal.

421
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:24,520
The bride was missing.

422
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:25,760
Maybe

423
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:27,640
she was dead.

424
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,080
What you said

425
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:35,760
is a good subject for a murder story.

426
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:36,960
But

427
00:18:37,080 --> 00:18:39,480
I don't write
that kind of story book anymore.

428
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:41,400
What?

429
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:43,140
Why don't you write?

430
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:44,240
I thought

431
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:47,560
you only wrote this kind of story book.

432
00:18:48,360 --> 00:18:49,640
For those stories,

433
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:51,060
they all came true.

434
00:18:51,060 --> 00:18:52,900
Go off.

435
00:18:52,900 --> 00:18:54,260
You really are

436
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:56,680
an evil person.

437
00:18:57,380 --> 00:18:59,840
Why don't you get out of Jinzhou?

438
00:19:00,340 --> 00:19:01,360
Go home.

439
00:19:01,820 --> 00:19:03,420
- Go away.
- Today,

440
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:06,260
I will eliminate the evil for the people

441
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:07,440
of Jinzhou.

442
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,360
- Awesome.
- Bravo.

443
00:19:19,360 --> 00:19:20,280
Bravo.

444
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:33,140
Bravo.

445
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,520
Bravo.

