00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,320
Thank you all for your support.

449
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:50,120
If you don't have anything else to do,

450
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:51,280
you can dismiss.

451
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:55,320
Ms. Gong.

452
00:19:55,760 --> 00:19:58,040
I thought you always hated me.

453
00:19:58,760 --> 00:19:59,600
Today,

454
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,000
why did you stand up for me?

455
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,600
I've always hated you.

456
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:05,920
But I didn't expect you to be so brave
to save Mr. Yu that day.

457
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:07,640
For that,

458
00:20:08,080 --> 00:20:09,280
it surprised me.

459
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,480
If you are all right, I will go first.

460
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:15,200
Ms. Gong.

461
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:17,800
The peach blossom brew
in Lu's Book Club is great.

462
00:20:18,120 --> 00:20:19,200
Would you like to have a taste?

463
00:20:19,320 --> 00:20:20,000
Drinking?

464
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:21,440
Fine.

465
00:20:22,820 --> 00:20:26,100
[Lu's Book Club]

466
00:20:39,520 --> 00:20:40,400
Lord Lin.

467
00:20:41,120 --> 00:20:42,120
Such a rare guest.

468
00:20:43,120 --> 00:20:43,960
Where's Ms. Lu?

469
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:46,360
Lord Lin.

470
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:48,440
If you are here to drink
and watch a play,

471
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:49,560
then go ahead.

472
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:51,960
But if you want to cause Lu trouble,

473
00:20:52,400 --> 00:20:53,880
please go away.

474
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:55,600
Of course,

475
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:57,420
I am here to drink and watch a play.

476
00:20:58,480 --> 00:20:59,520
I am wondering

477
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:01,400
if Mr. Fu could drink with me?

478
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:16,480
Mr. Fu, are you good

479
00:21:17,120 --> 00:21:18,040
at drinking?

480
00:21:19,120 --> 00:21:19,920
Just so-so.

481
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:21,840
But I am better

482
00:21:22,520 --> 00:21:23,840
than you.

483
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:31,440
Hey.

484
00:21:32,080 --> 00:21:33,560
You jerk.

485
00:21:33,760 --> 00:21:36,200
How dare you seduce my wife?

486
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:39,000
Hey.

487
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,640
I am so angry.

488
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:55,240
You're gonna lose.

489
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:57,120
You wish.

490
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:09,640
Lord Lin is so good
at playing the finger-guessing game.

491
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:10,600
My Lord.

492
00:22:11,080 --> 00:22:13,000
You and Ms. Lu love each other.

493
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:15,360
Why don't you show your love?

494
00:22:17,320 --> 00:22:22,920
I'll see you off.

495
00:22:24,440 --> 00:22:25,800
I was playful when I was young.

496
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:27,840
I ran up the hill and got hurt.

497
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:29,680
There I met Lu.

498
00:22:30,320 --> 00:22:31,800
She carried me back.

499
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,400
And since then we've been playmates.

500
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:35,920
But due to family status,

501
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:38,880
I could only sneak out to play with her.

502
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:42,240
I'm just a merchant's daughter.

503
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:43,000
[Lu's Book Club]

504
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:43,760
But

505
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:46,120
he is the son of a noble family.

506
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:47,680
I thought

507
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:49,960
we could go on like that.

508
00:22:51,080 --> 00:22:52,840
But when he was 20 years old,

509
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:56,640
his mother made him an engagement.

510
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:59,020
Do you mean

511
00:22:59,040 --> 00:23:01,440
the daughter of the prime minister,
Wen Ruoxi?

512
00:23:02,880 --> 00:23:03,640
Exactly.

513
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:05,800
I have only

514
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:08,640
Lu in my heart
from the beginning to the end.

515
00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:10,400
And only she

516
00:23:11,520 --> 00:23:12,720
can be my wife.

517
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:15,320
So I refused

518
00:23:15,560 --> 00:23:16,640
the family arrangements

519
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:18,680
to marry Ms. Wen.

520
00:23:19,520 --> 00:23:20,360
So

521
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:21,560
I made an appointment

522
00:23:21,680 --> 00:23:22,560
with Lu.

523
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:25,280
We were leaving the capital.

524
00:23:26,120 --> 00:23:26,800
Tomorrow,

525
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:28,760
we will still meet here.

526
00:23:29,080 --> 00:23:30,040
Let's get out of here together.

527
00:23:31,080 --> 00:23:32,000
The world is big.

528
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:34,200
There will be a place for us.

529
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:35,920
Yes.

530
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:39,400
You guys agreed to elope.

531
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,040
And then?

532
00:23:41,520 --> 00:23:43,560
We made an appointment
to meet at the Lake Pavilion.

533
00:23:45,520 --> 00:23:47,040
But I waited there for a long time.

534
00:23:48,280 --> 00:23:51,280
[Farewell Letter]
Finally, a farewell letter came.

535
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:54,440
But I was delayed
by some trivial matter.

536
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:56,520
By the time I got there,

537
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:59,200
there had been no one
at the Lake Pavilion.

538
00:24:00,300 --> 00:24:01,480
[Farewell Letter]

539
00:24:01,480 --> 00:24:04,480
Only a farewell letter sent by her.

540
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:07,080
My Lord.

541
00:24:07,800 --> 00:24:09,080
Have you ever thought about it?

542
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:11,920
What if this farewell letter
wasn't written by her?

543
00:24:12,840 --> 00:24:14,040
I also doubted it.

544
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,240
But the handwriting

545
00:24:17,800 --> 00:24:18,800
was hers.

546
00:24:19,280 --> 00:24:20,160
Wait.

547
00:24:21,120 --> 00:24:22,720
Wasn't it you

548
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:24,720
who gave the farewell letter to Qingqiu?

549
00:24:26,960 --> 00:24:28,400
Your cousin

550
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:32,140
is only good at lying to you.

551
00:24:32,560 --> 00:24:33,660
Impossible.

552
00:24:33,660 --> 00:24:35,400
Qingqiu wouldn't lie.

553
00:24:36,080 --> 00:24:37,840
I didn't think he was lying.

554
00:24:38,560 --> 00:24:40,200
I would like to ask him for that.

555
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:42,560
When I went there
with the servant of the Wang family

556
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,760
to find out what happened,

557
00:24:46,120 --> 00:24:47,800
I saw Lin Qingqiu board the Lake Island,

558
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:50,360
and Wen Ruoxi was there.

559
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:52,640
I wanted to go after him,

560
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:54,880
but the two of them
were talking and laughing.

561
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,720
They seem to be very intimate.

562
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:05,320
Haven't you ever thought
of looking for Ms. Lu?

563
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:07,240
Of course, I have.

564
00:25:08,080 --> 00:25:09,760
But she just disappeared.

565
00:25:10,840 --> 00:25:12,000
[Lu Residence]
I couldn't find her anywhere.

566
00:25:16,600 --> 00:25:17,680
Mr. Lin.

567
00:25:18,360 --> 00:25:19,680
You should come back.

568
00:25:20,360 --> 00:25:21,280
If it weren't for you,

569
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:23,600
my lady wouldn't have run away.

570
00:25:23,720 --> 00:25:24,920
Lord Lu and Mrs. Lu

571
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:26,400
won't see you.

572
00:25:27,480 --> 00:25:28,600
Then I got a serious illness

573
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:30,040
and missed the Imperial Examination.

574
00:25:31,040 --> 00:25:31,840
Then

575
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,960
I heard Ms. Lu's story books.

576
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:37,680
I guessed it might be her.

577
00:25:38,520 --> 00:25:39,240
So

578
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:41,760
I asked the emperor
to give me an official position.

579
00:25:43,360 --> 00:25:44,480
